<title>Wonderful, Wonderful</title>
<aka>Underfull, underfull</aka>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Underfull, underfull,
 Jesus er for meg.
 Rådgiver, Fredsfyrste,
 Mektig Gud Han er.
 Frelste meg, bevarer meg,
 fra all synd og skam.
 Underfull er min Gjenløser,
 pris Hans Navn.

[V2]
 Wonderful, wonderful,
 Jesus is to me.
 Counselor, Prince of Peace,
 Mighty God is He.
 Saving me, keeping me
 from all sin and shame.
 Wonderful is my Redeemer,
 Praise His name!</lyrics>
</song>